Two original references for Blue Waters Architecture and Capabilites can be found at 

1.     Brett Bode, Michelle Butler, Thom Dunning, William Gropp, Torsten Hoe- fler, Wen-mei Hwu, and William Kramer (alphabetical). The Blue Waters Super-System for Super-Science. Contemporary HPC Architectures, Jeffery Vetter editor. Sitka Publications, November 2012.Edited by Jeffrey S . Vetter, Chapman and Hall/CRC 2013, Print ISBN: 978-1-4665-6834-1, eBook ISBN: 978-1-4665-6835-8

2.     Kramer, William, Michelle Butler, Gregory Bauer, Kalyana Chadalavada, Celso Mendes, Blue Waters Parallel I/O Storage Sub-system, High Performance Parallel I/O, Prabhat and Quincey Koziol editors, CRC Publications, Taylor and Francis Group, Boca Raton FL, 2015, Hardback Print ISBN 13:978-1-4665-8234-7.
